{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>[Background]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Congratulations on starting your CEO career!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We\u2019re here to teach you how to manage the relationship between you and your secretary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you happen to experience anything else, well... that\u2019s just your imagination running wild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_TrailerCover_Steam_-_Fin.png?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>  <br>[Game Feature]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif3.1.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>VR Secretary</i>, you will become a rookie CEO, managing not just the office, but also the subtle dynamics with your new secretary, Ailey. Here\u2019s what awaits you:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Roleplay:</strong> Take charge as a fresh CEO navigating a fully interactive VR office. From delegating tasks to sharing quiet moments after work, every scene brings you closer to the fine line between professionalism and personal connection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Scenarios:</strong> From managing tasks in the office to sharing drinks after hours\u2014every choice matters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>High Interaction: </strong>Explore a variety of poses and enjoy the freedom to interact closely with your secretary, creating a highly immersive experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>[Tips]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Before\u00a0you begin the first day as a CEO, here are some <strong>practical tips</strong> to keep in mind:<br><strong>Tip 1</strong>: Be polite and keep a professional distance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif1.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tip 2</strong>:\u00a0Maintain proper social etiquette, even when drinking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif2.2.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif2.1.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tip 3</strong>: Once everything is organized,\u00a0your career will reach the next level!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif3.4.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Prove you can stay cool, make the right calls, and survive the ultimate workplace challenge - if you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thank you for playing VR Secretary. We hope you enjoy every moment of your office journey!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737438407","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737438407","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/2c9a8ed201d991fdcdc33e71dc03c5d94c213707/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737438407","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/2c9a8ed201d991fdcdc33e71dc03c5d94c213707/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737438407","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"VR Only","id":54}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"