fessional distance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif1.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tip 2</strong>:\u00a0Maintain proper social etiquette, even when drinking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif2.2.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif2.1.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tip 3</strong>: Once everything is organized,\u00a0your career will reach the next level!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/extras/AileyVR_Gif3.4.gif?t=1737438407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Prove you can stay cool, make the right calls, and survive the ultimate workplace challenge - if you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thank you for playing VR Secretary. We hope you enjoy every moment of your office journey!</p>","developers":["Stargazers"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384220/header.jpg?t=1737438407","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257083076,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2570830